<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Kingainiem Isu bang guol dang umlo,
 Khatcha le! khatcha le!
 Midang thagau na hihdam thei umlo,
 Khatcha le! khatcha le!

[V2]
 Isu'n I gimtheihnau cheng A he'i,
 Nitum masieh ei pui ina;
 Kingainiem Isu bang guol dang umlo,
 Khatcha le! khatcha le!

[V3]
 2. Amah bang guol sang leh thiengtho umlo,
 Khatcha le! khatcha le!
 Amah bang kingainiem guol dang umlo,
 Khatcha le! khatcha le!

[V4]
 3. I kawma a naihloh tik a um puo'i,
 Khatvei le! khatvei le!
 A kipahsak zawhloh thimna umlo,
 Khatvei le! khatvei le!

[V5]
 4. Zie Guol hin mi A hengilh kha ngei em??
 Khatvei le! khatvei le!
 Mi gilo lak nuomloh tik A nei em?
 Khatvei le! khatvei le!

[V6]
 5. Hukdampa piek bang thildang a um em?
 Khatcha le! khatcha le!
 Van Ina I chen dinguh ei niel dem?
 Niel lo ding! niel lo ding!</lyrics>
<title>NO, NOT ONE !</title>
<hymn_number>65</hymn_number>
</song>